nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|In 5@C, we lose 1 heart, 1 diamond, 1 club, and 2 spades for down 3. So doubled at this vul, is better than letting them make 4@H since it is -500 instead of -620.|
